notes.title: Mahadeva
notes.label: Education
notes.textData: The DOCX to HTML converter provides a REST API for converting the Microsoft Word files to HTML documents. The service generates HTML data and returns it to the API consumer, allowing it to display it in the browser or inside a CKEditor 5 instance. It can be used to automate the conversion of Word files and allows for mass documents conversion with the omission of the editor.
